Abstract = {{Recognizing the identity of a person is fundamental to guide social
   interactions. We can recognize the identity of a person looking at her
   face, but also listening to her voice. An important question concerns
   how visual and auditory information come together, enabling us to
   recognize identity independently of the modality of the stimulus. This
